msgstr "https://github.com/headwalluk/tidy-resize-images"

#. Description of the plugin
#: tidy-resize-images.php
msgid "Keep the WordPress Media Library lean. Resize oversized uploads, convert unsuitable formats, and recompress bloated files — with originals safely backed up to a Trash directory, dry-run preview, and full WP-CLI control."
msgstr "Keep the WordPress Media Library lean. Resize oversized uploads, convert unsuitable formats, and recompress bloated files — with originals safely backed up to a Trash directory, dry-run preview, and full WP-CLI control."

